<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="bear-keep-in-mind">bear / keep … in mind</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-bear-keep-in-mind-that">1.<strong>将…记在心中；记起 (bear / keep in mind that)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It’s a good idea — I’ll bear it in mind. 
这是个好主意，我会记在心里的。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Whenever or however you take notes, keep in mind that note-taking is a selective process. 
不管何时以何种方式记笔记，你都要记住，记笔记是个有选择性的过程。</p><footer> 2008 全国</footer></div></div>